channel.description: The latest CVEs for SAP SE -- SAP NetWeaver AS ABAP (Web Dynpro)

item.title: CVE-2020-26819|2024-08-04T16:03:23.072Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20as%20abap%20%28web%20dynpro%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS ABAP (Web Dynpro), versions - 731, 740, 750, 751, 752, 753, 754, 755, 782, allows an authenticated user to access Web Dynpro components, that allows them to read and delete database logfiles because of Improper Access Control.

item.title: CVE-2020-26818|2024-08-04T16:03:22.370Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20as%20abap%20%28web%20dynpro%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS ABAP (Web Dynpro), versions - 731, 740, 750, 751, 752, 753, 754, 755, 782, allows an authenticated user to access Web Dynpro components, which reveals sensitive system information that would otherwise be restricted to highly privileged users because of missing authorization, resulting in Information Disclosure.
